OL,3,CFamily's tribute to man who died after
OL,4,Cbeing shot in the face
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died after
OL,7,Fbeing shot at a flat in have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to him.
OL,10,FPeter Hale, 50, was targeted at an
OL,11,Faddress in Haslingden Close in the Old
OL,12,FSwan area in January. He was shot in
OL,13,Fthe face and airlifted to hospital but
OL,14,Fdied of his injuries in hospital.
OL,16,FIn the statement, Mr Hale's family
OL,17,Fsaid: "No words can describe the loss
OL,18,Fwe as a family are feeling following
OL,19,Fthe tragic death of Peter a loving
OL,20,Fson, brother and uncle.
