OL,6,F"He was a happy-go-lucky type of man
OL,7,Fthat has been taken by an act of gun
OL,8,Fviolence. Rest in peace. You will be
OL,9,Fin our hearts forever."
OL,11,FMr Hale's family are being supported
OL,12,Fby specially trained officers.
OL,14,FShay Walker, 25, of Stoneycroft in
OL,15,FLiverpool, was charged with murder and
OL,16,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,17,Fendanger life. He has been remanded in
OL,18,Fcustody after appearing before a court
