OL,6,FIn a statement issued on Sunday,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Jason Pye,
OL,8,Fof , said: "Our thoughts and
OL,9,Fcondolences are with the family of the
OL,10,Fvictim who has sadly died today.
OL,11,FAlthough a man has been charged, our
OL,12,Finvestigation is ongoing and we are
OL,13,Fstill appealing for anyone with
OL,14,Finformation about this incident to
OL,15,Fplease get in touch.
